{"tid":445974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃之鋒羅冠聰獲准保釋","createTime":"2017-10-24T01:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T14:34:11.000Z","uid":136994,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"b6c7c2d8c04f23c5775166ec33638b53ad4a0211","tid":445974,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:45:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171024/57369455\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171024%2F57369455&d=u9KxolH6fjab1lnHyOyfZQHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7591a32c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171024%2F57369455&h=e4a172f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171024/57369455</a><br />\n<br />\n雙學三子黃之鋒、羅冠聰、周永康於2014年發起重奪公民廣場，被裁定非法集結等罪成立，3人原被判社會服務令或緩刑，但上訴庭改判3人監禁6至8個月。黃之鋒及羅冠聰在服刑逾兩個月後，今向終審法院申請保釋等候上訴，律政司一方表示不反對申請，終院首席法官馬道立准許兩人保釋直至上訴有結果。<br />\n<br />\n原審時，黃之鋒、周永康被裁定非法集結罪成，黃被判80小時社會服務令，周被判監3周，緩刑一年。而羅冠聰則被裁定煽惑他人參與非法集結罪成，被判120小時社會服務令。惟上訴庭於今年8月17日改判黃、周及羅分別入獄6、7、8個月。"},{"pid":"97a25dbfb2c42506ae86fe3282453ec42142d635","tid":445974,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:46:10.000Z","msg":"律政司仲唔追擊？"},{"pid":"4f8f4e25bf84c58b98e4d2ff48da572fb2794a0a","tid":445974,"uid":51904,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"狂賀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ea9a486d701f29af6b23a9eb22f33b8e2c9e29","tid":445974,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:51:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4551667e66473ec6c8d364c54ee8cef382ddbb7a","tid":445974,"uid":44309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T01:56:51.000Z","msg":"今次佢哋上訴應該正苦會俾佢哋贏，因為點都屈佢哋坐咗兩個月監，然後又塞住全世界把口話政治檢控，香港法治已死哩類話。"},